nodes.text: This planet was the location of the Wilds, a swampy overgrown jungle. A settlement was located seventeen kilometers from the Wilds. The planet had a native predator, the corvaj. During a training patrol, Ranna Gorjaye and Calson crashed on the planet after Calson crowded the formation and clipped Gorjaye's wing. Calson was killed by a corvaj after refusing to follow Gorjaye's commands on the ground.
